<span id="Description"></span>
==Beschreibung==

Das Werkzeug [[Image:BIM_SetWPSide.svg|24px]] [[BIM_SetWPSide/de|BIM SetWPSide]] legt die Arbeitsebene auf die globale YZ-Ebene (Seitenriss).

<span id="Usage"></span>
==Anwendung==

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Snapping → [[Image:BIM_SetWPSide.svg|16px]] Working Plane Side}} option from the menu.
#* Right-click in the [[3D_view|3D view]] and select the {{MenuCommand|Snapping → [[Image:BIM_SetWPSide.svg|16px]] Working Plane Side}} option from the context menu.
#* Use the keyboard shortcut: {{KEY|W}} then {{KEY|P}}, then {{KEY|3}}.
</div>


